{"tid":1561371,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"牧童笛 We Connect","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:50:48.000Z","uid":167144,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"720a0dc257e8ed43997cb5b1daa9c2c607467f0e","tid":1561371,"uid":167144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"以前係屋企吹牧童笛(吹下D詩歌、流行曲咁)<br />\n成日比呀哥鬧叫我咪嘈<br />\n吹多幾分鐘就會<br />\n發晒脾氣咁鬧我，好似想打我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日係屋企吹《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n吹左勁多次<br />\n估唔到呀哥冇出過一句聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近日既事都令到同呀哥講多左野,<br />\n雖然只不過係由冇對話，變成依家都有一兩句,<br />\n仲試過同呀哥一齊同深藍屋企人嘈，當然我地都冇辦法改變到佢地諗法<br />\n<br />\n細個果陣，因為屋企得一部電腦會爭機打，之後嘈交。<br />\n有時我霸住唔讓比佢，仲會出手打我<br />\n我太瘦唔夠佢打，佢用果陣我只能夠打比呀媽求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望能夠同呀哥關係越來越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然改變唔到深藍嘅上一輩，覺得有點冇力，<br />\n但好感恩有呢個呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n共勉之<br />\n<br />\n未敢係屋企人面前吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b66ef7a5c78596868c6fb23a122778e8d6fff57","tid":1561371,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOSjYn.jpg&h=c1edffca&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeMP6D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeMP6D2.jpg&h=0810fe9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPmXLP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPmXLP.png&h=5f6e170e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYO68T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYO68T8.jpg&h=b22b9f08&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"efd38aa56c88cea1606778390dbbfd4eceae6b49","tid":1561371,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\